org.xchain.framework.servlet

Class XChainManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • org.xchain.framework.servlet.XChainManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public class XChainManager
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
    This is an INCOMPLETE servlet management interface for the xchains framework. Currently, all that this servlet supports is the rendering of xchain files with all xchain-stylesheet processing instructions rendered.
    Author:
    Christian Trimble, John Trimble, Josh Kennedy
